  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个HealthTech系统的架构图，核心是患者记录模块。我设想用一个子图把LabAnalyzer和HIPAA_Vault包在一起，命名为HealthTech_PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pezkuwi",
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiRuntime"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，子图叫HealthTech_PatientRecords。里面放两个节点：HealthTech_LabAnalyzer和HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault。我注意到这两个内部节点的显示文本有重叠，LabAnalyzer出现了两次，这是故意的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiSDK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这是有意的设计。PezkuwiNode代表LabAnalyzer的核心计算实例，而PezkuwiSDK是另一个独立的LabAnalyzer组件，虽然显示名称相同，但功能不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PezkuwiNode",
        "PezkuwiSDK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，子图已经画好。现在外部连接怎么处理？我看到还有一个FRAME节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRAME",
        "Pezkuwi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FRAME是前端框架，它需要和HIPAA_Vault建立虚线连接，表示配置或监控关系，但不是直接数据流。另外PezkuwiSDK也要和PezkuwiNode用虚线连接，表示SDK调用核心实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRAME",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "PezkuwiSDK",
        "PezkuwiNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：FRAME虚线连到PezkuwiRuntime（HIPAA_Vault），PezkuwiSDK虚线连到PezkuwiNode（LabAnalyzer）。方向都是从左到右吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRAME",
        "PezkuwiRuntime",
        "PezkuwiSDK",
        "PezkuwiNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，整体布局用LR从左到右。FRAME在子图左边，PezkuwiSDK可以放在子图右边或下方，只要能清晰表达调用关系就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FRAME",
        "Pezkuwi",
        "PezkuwiSDK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
